title: One Acre In The Country! Everything You Could Want 100
text:
One Acre In The Country! Everything You Could Want 100 ad date: 10/17/2015 
One Acre In The Country! Everything You Could Want 100 Marie Lane, Crescent City, CA Beautiful home on one acre in the country, out of the fog belt and 5 minutes from Crescent City. 768 sq ft detached garage with 13' over-head door. This 2-story Victorian style home is 2817 sq ft & well cared for. Floor plan allows for a family room off kitchen, formal living and dining, grand entryway, granite counter-tops, garden window, double ovens, large breakfast bar, sun tunnels, French doors, terraces, hobbie room, guest quarters, well house and there is extensive storage throughout the home. No. 1365074 $459,000
